  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to investigate the effectiveness and acceptability of the multi-level
      pregnancy test for self-assessment of abortion outcomes, without a routine provider contact.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
